<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Xtrabackup - 标签 - _浅行</title><link>https://liwanggui.com/tags/xtrabackup/</link><description>Xtrabackup - 标签 - _浅行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>liwanggui@163.com (李王贵)</managingEditor><webMaster>liwanggui@163.com (李王贵)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Jan 2021 14:41:02 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://liwanggui.com/tags/xtrabackup/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MySQL GTID 从库快速恢复</title><link>https://liwanggui.com/posts/mysql-restore-gtid-replication/</link><pubDate>Wed, 13 Jan 2021 14:41:02 +0800</pubDate><author><name>李王贵</name></author><guid>https://liwanggui.com/posts/mysql-restore-gtid-replication/</guid><description>备份主库为了节省恢复的时间我们使用 xtrabackup 备份主库，然后拷贝到从库再将数据恢复到从库中 完整备份主库 bash # 备份 xtrabackup --defaults-file=/usr/local/mysql/etc/my.cnf -S /data/mysql/mysql.sock -u root -p --backup --target-dir=/data/backup 恢复主从复制 恢复从库数</description></item><item><title>Xtrabackup 备份 MySQL (全备)</title><link>https://liwanggui.com/posts/xtrabackup-backup-mysql/</link><pubDate>Mon, 04 Jan 2021 11:08:35 +0800</pubDate><author><name>李王贵</name></author><guid>https://liwanggui.com/posts/xtrabackup-backup-mysql/</guid><description>percona-xtrabackup 是物理备份工具，拷贝数据文件。 原生态支持全备和增量备份。 会记录二进制日志文件及位置。 InnoDB 表: 热备份，业务正常发生时，影响较小的备份方式 非 InnoDB 表</description></item></channel></rss>